      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Theh annual meeting of the\nWashington State Horticultural So\nciety, now in session in Spokane,\nwill close this afternoon with cleo\nton of officers and selection of a\nplace of assembly next year. A\nnumber of topics of special inter-\nest to fruit growers are on the\nclosing day program. The society's\nmeeting here has been unusually\nsuccessful, the attendance of about\n400 members demonstrating the\nImportance the fruit industry has\nalready attained in this state."
